My thoughts exactly, the raw damage from crossbow will also produces stronger crits than the crit damage +15% from gakkung. From further research and asking around I saw that people who played before on CN suggests gakkung becuase it retains the price better there than mystery bow. 

&amp;#x200B;

Did a quick price check and a +10gakkung \[2\] there with 4th enchantment is still 14m. While a +6Mystery bow \[2\] is only 5m at CN.

&amp;#x200B;

So its a wiser investment for a 2 slotted weapon than buying a 2 slot mystery bow now worth 17m-20m. I think I would go to the 2 slot +10crossbow with good enchantment for now.
